body_html:
This sounds like a similar problem to #5670. In this case, protoc isn't re-running, I'm guessing you've done an earlier build based on an old version of tensorflow\core\framework\types.proto, and the PIP package contains a mixture of code based on that old version and new code that expects to see the new types.

Your best bet (in the short term) is probably to delete the entire tf_python directory to force a rebuild.

body:
This sounds like a similar problem to #5670. In this case, `protoc` isn't re-running, I'm guessing you've done an earlier build based on an old version of `tensorflow\core\framework\types.proto`, and the PIP package contains a mixture of code based on that old version and new code that expects to see the new types.

Your best bet (in the short term) is probably to delete the entire `tf_python` directory to force a rebuild.
